  "bio_raw": "She has seven years of teaching experience. She worked as a lecturer in the Department of Computer Science & Engineering at Daffodil International University from 2015-2019. Then she was promoted to senior lecturer and was there till June 2022. Prior to this, she worked as a lecturer (Contractual) in the Department of Computer Science & Engineering at Daffodil International University for four months. She also worked as a lecturer (ad hoc) at East West University. She earned her B.Sc. and M.Sc. degrees in CSE from the Department of Computer Science & Engineering at Jahangirnagar University.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Computer Vision, Image Processing, Machine Learning"
  ],
  "education": [
